SUMMARY:International Karaoke Night @ I-House
DESCRIPTION:International Karaoke Night is a high energy celebration of music\, culture\, and community in Davis. Sing songs from around the world — from favorites from your home country to global hits and timeless classics. No karaoke experience required! Everyone is welcome! \nThis evening is all about fun and connection\, not performance. Come solo or with friends. Sing your heart out\, cheer others on\, hit the dance floor\, or simply soak in the atmosphere in a welcoming\, low pressure space. Between performances\, there will be line dancing and raffle prizes given away! \nDiscover music in different languages\, meet new people\, and take part in a joyful evening that brings cultures together through shared experience. Get your ticket and join us for a night where community is built one song at a time.
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/international-karaoke-night-i-house/
LOCATION:International House Davis\, 10 College Park\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://visitdavis.org/wp-content/uploads/International-Karaoke-Flyer-Website-1-V4mWs4.png
ORGANIZER;CN="International House Davis":MAILTO:shahzana@ihousedavis.org
END:VEVENT
